# Group Committees
Represents the committees formed in both the senate and the house.

---
**Committee attributes:**
- id `(String)` : Id of committee.
- name `(String)` : Name of committee.
- chair `(String)` : Committee chair.
- chamber `(String)` : Which chamber of congress member is part of.
- num_members `(Integer)` : Number of members on the committee.

---
## Committee Collection [comittees]
### List all committees [GET]
Retrieve all committees of current congress

+ curl "https://api.eklogi.me/comittees/"

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
