# Group Bills
Represents the bills introduced in the both the senate and house.

---
**Bill attributes:**
- id `(String)` : Id of bill.
- name `(String)`: Official title for bill
- date `(String)`: Date when bill was introduced
- primare_subject `(String)`: Main subject of the bill
- chamber `(String)`: Chamber where the bill was introduced
- house_passage_date `(String)`: Date the bill passed on House
- senate_passage_date `(String)`: Date the bill passed on Senate

---
## Bill Collection [bills]
### List all bills [GET]
Retrieve all bills introduced during the current congress.

