# Group Votes
Represents the detailed votes for specific bills introduced in the both the senate and house.

---
**Votes attributes:**
- id `(String)' : Id of bill on this vote.
- session `(String): Session where vote was casted
- chamber `(String): Chamber where the vote was casted
- question `(String): Question surrounding the bill
- result `(String): Result of the vote
- date `(String): Date when this vote happened
- time `(String): Time the vote was casted
---
## Votes Collection [votes]
### List all votes [GET]
Retrieve all votes on every bill introduced during the current congress.

+ curl "https://api.eklogi.me/votes"

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": "hr21-115",
                "session": "1",
                "chamber": "House",
                "question": "On the Motion",
                "result": "Motion Rejected",
                "date": "2017-01-11",
                "time": "22:07:00"
            }, 
            
            {
                "id": "hr210-115",
                "title": "Native American Energy Act",
                "chamber": "House"
                "question": "On the Motion",
                "result": "Motion Rejected",
                "date": "2017-01-11",
                "time": "21:17:00"
            }
            ...
        ]

